transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes, is this SCORE Blue?

Speaker 1: This is SCORE Blue, yes.

Speaker 1: who's possibly interested in purchasing a sample,

Speaker 2: just to see how they work.

Speaker 1: Sure, I can help you out with that.

Speaker 2: Tim, can you just confirm your date of birth?

Speaker 1: 3-6-1967, I'm probably in your system

Speaker 2: because I'm already getting the outlets from you.

Speaker 1: Yes, I do see you ordered with us in the past.

Speaker 2: Are you still at 1005 Old Mill Creek Court?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: All right, perfect.

Speaker 1: Yeah, so we have the AGV,

Speaker 2: you can get a quantity of 40 for 163.95,

Speaker 1: then we have a quantity of 25 for 113.95,

Speaker 2: and a quantity of 10 for 63.95.

Speaker 1: What is the largest quantity in place?

Speaker 2: A quantity of 40 for 163.95.

Speaker 1: Okay, yeah, let me try that out and see how that works.

Speaker 2: Okay, no problem.

Speaker 1: Give me one second.

Speaker 2: And I did want to check to see

Speaker 1: if you guys also had brand Cialis.

Speaker 2: I know that there's a lot of generic,

Speaker 1: I get Cialis from you, but I don't get enough,

Speaker 2: I have to go to an outside source to get more.

Speaker 1: Oh, let me see.

Speaker 2: No, we just have generic Cialis.

Speaker 1: Yeah, we don't have the branded.

Speaker 2: Okay, all right, let me go back to the other screen.

Speaker 1: And then the other thing that I've tried finding

Speaker 2: and buying from you guys a number of times

Speaker 1: is the RO Sparks,

Speaker 2: and maybe I would get some of those too

Speaker 1: in this order if I could.

Speaker 2: Those are the only two that I haven't tried,

Speaker 1: I think, that are heavily marketed on Fox News Network.

Speaker 2: The RO, I think that's a different company.

Speaker 1: Okay, I thought it might be through Scorblue.

Speaker 2: What's it called again?

Speaker 1: I know we have a couple of different companies,

Speaker 2: but I just work on the Scorblue side.

Speaker 1: What was it called again?

Speaker 2: I think it's RO.Sparks, S-P-A-R-K-S.com,

Speaker 1: and I thought it was with the same company,

Speaker 2: but no, that's a different company.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Yeah, that's a different ED medication.

Speaker 1: Oh, that's the one where they blend

Speaker 2: the Denafil and Tadatafil.

Speaker 1: Yeah, they're not FDA approved,

Speaker 2: but if it works for you, that's good.

Speaker 1: Okay, so, okay, we got a quantity of 40, 100 milligrams.

Speaker 2: Are we still using your Visa ending in 7815?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: Okay, perfect.

Speaker 1: You know, I have another one that I can use.

Speaker 2: I mean, actually, that's a company card.

Speaker 1: I put that on there because it actually has...

Speaker 2: No problem, that one went through.

Speaker 1: It's part of a prescription.

Speaker 2: I call it medication.

Speaker 1: Is it safe to identify that in this way?

Speaker 2: Is it what?

Speaker 1: And will it show up on the credit card as ED medicine?

Speaker 2: No, it will show up as SCORE Blue LLC.

Speaker 1: Okay, let's try it then.

Speaker 2: Let's go ahead and put it through there.

Speaker 1: All right, perfect.

Speaker 2: It already went through,

Speaker 1: so they'll be shipping that out to you today.

Speaker 2: Okay, that sounds good.

Speaker 1: And anything else that's new?

Speaker 2: I mean, I do get the generic Cialis through you guys,

Speaker 1: but I also go online, order brand Cialis

Speaker 2: whenever I can get it.

Speaker 1: Okay, good.

Speaker 2: All right, perfect.

Speaker 1: Well, you're all set, Tim.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you very much.

Speaker 1: And you've got my address?

Speaker 2: You want to confirm the address?

Speaker 1: Yes, 1005 Old Mill Creek Court,

Speaker 2: Raleigh, North Carolina, 27614?

Speaker 1: Yes, that's correct.

Speaker 2: All right, perfect.

Speaker 1: You're all set.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you.

Speaker 1: No problem, bye.
